{"tid":1861332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正視聽：賀一誠只係正常表現，係林奠太撚癲","createTime":"2020-02-04T05:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T06:36:25.000Z","uid":90601,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"056a737c8e742ec3c3ec6f4a97821d74614b7d21","tid":1861332,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"瘟疫係非常時期 大家做咩都只係想保命<br />\n唔否認賀一誠今次決斷力係比林奠強 但佢既施政只係正常表現<br />\n封強國人封賭場停課派錢依啲係人都識做<br />\n係柒婆唔到最後一刻都唔做 逼到香港人著曬火<br />\n比較之下 大家可以盡情屌柒林奠 但唔需要過份吹奏賀一誠<br />\n<br />\n當然後唔排除一切都係中共既劇本 要扶澳滅港"},{"pid":"78521970056caace9fd4346acd956e1aa2361fc6","tid":1861332,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17a12e14a1ee77b6a642cc23083b59049670b24","tid":1861332,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:45:21.000Z","msg":"大家千奇千奇唔好再吹奏<br />\n我認為係一個局黎 柒婆係有意做得有咁仆街得咁仆街<br />\n而澳門條鳩佬亦係有咁好扮到咁好<br />\n就係想你地比較 然後吹奏 <br />\n唔好唔記得我地要打既係共產黨 唔係柒婆"},{"pid":"78a9a8acfced079186db40821320362a6814a1a2","tid":1861332,"uid":15193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:45:33.000Z","msg":"正視聽 賀一誠同林鄭一樣 都係聽中央指示"},{"pid":"e78ce2832df07ef385786881e554fc23134331e7","tid":1861332,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推<br />\n<br />\n借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[行動post] 武漢肺炎係上天賜比香港人打爆港共嘅機會，做嘢啦！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1838198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1838198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"